Lingua/JA/Mail/Header version 0.01
===========================

 This module is used to build ISO-2022-JP charset 'B' encoding
 mail header fields.

INSTALLATION

 To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

 This module requires perl5.8 or later.

 This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Encode
   MIME::Base64

